  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You may craft your destructive blast into a 5-foot-by-5-foot cubic wall with a duration of concentration, so long as it is fully contained within your destructive blast range. You may spend a spell point to increase this effect and create a wall up to 20 feet high and up to 20 feet wide per caster level in a straight line, or a hemisphere with a radius up to 5 feet per 2 caster levels (minimum 5 feet). If used in either way, the duration increases to 1 round per caster level.</p>\n<p>The wall does not block line of effect, line of sight, projectiles, or thrown objects. Creatures passing through your wall suffer your destructive blast&#8217;s damage and effects as normal. Creatures standing in the wall&#8217;s space when it is created are allowed a Reflex save to avoid damage.</p>\n",
